<plot>Based on the hit TV show, you take on the role of CIA/Alliance double agent Sydney Bristow in this third-person game using her cunning, extensive knowledge of martial arts and array of high-tech gadgetry to accomplish dangerous missions. Alias, the game, will encompass all of the key elements behind the series' success, including high-action combat, stealth missions and time-based objectives, espionage, intriguing plot twists, high-tech weaponry and stunning gameplay locations that span the globe.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?029699</url></doc>
